    "ChallengesDespite the widespread use of CADD and ML methods in the field of anesthetic drug discovery in recent years, the inherent disadvantages and limitations of these methods, along with the complexity of the anesthetic process, are still inescapable hurdles to the development of new anesthetic drugs."
